{
  "texts": [
    "These models can predict patient response to treatment and identify subgroups that are more likely to benefit from a drug.",
    "DL models can be used to develop personalized treatment plans based on an individual's genetic information, medical history, and other factors.",
    "These models can predict the effectiveness of different drugs and help healthcare providers make informed treatment decisions.",
    "DL models can be integrated with electronic health records to provide a comprehensive view of patient health and treatment outcomes.",
    "This can help healthcare providers make informed drug treatment and patient care decisions."
  ]
}